  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0db8\u0dd9\u0da7\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca \u0da7\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd3 \u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc0\u0dd2 \u0db8\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd0\u0dbd\u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Plans to buy 100,000 MT of Paddy from the Paddy Marketing Board",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Agriculture has said that the Paddy Marketing Board has planned to purchase 1 lakh metric tonnes of paddy from the yala season harvest.",
        "It is proposed to spend 10,500 million rupees for this purpose.",
        "The Ministry of Agriculture states that arrangements have been made to get Cabinet approval for that next week."
      ],
